Annotation on the envelope: "Rubens Vier Weltströme Wien" addressed (inside) to "Lehrstuhl und Institut für Kunstgeschichte Prof. Dr. phil. Evers 6100 Darmstadt Technische Hochschule" and dated 15.11.1967.

  • Notes about 'The Four Continents' in Vienna (dated 1967)

The inventory of 1993 also mentions reproductions, but these are missing and were probably taken out in the Rubenianum and filed in the Rubens documentation.
